{"words":[{"word":"huh","count":3},{"word":"everything","count":3},{"word":"exiles","count":2},{"word":"alright","count":2},{"word":"else","count":2},{"word":"keep","count":2},{"word":"hell","count":1},{"word":"coming","count":1},{"word":"push","count":1},{"word":"around","count":1},{"word":"w-wait","count":1},{"word":"second","count":1},{"word":"things","count":1},{"word":"violent","count":1},{"word":"talk","count":1},{"word":"okay","count":1},{"word":"mingyan","count":1},{"word":"men","count":1},{"word":"answer","count":1},{"word":"questions","count":1},{"word":"already","count":1},{"word":"swear","count":1},{"word":"i'll","count":1},{"word":"match","count":1},{"word":"male","count":1},{"word":"female","count":1},{"word":"ahead","count":1},{"word":"pick","count":1},{"word":"fight","count":1},{"word":"risking","count":1},{"word":"life","count":1},{"word":"ask","count":1},{"word":"oh","count":1},{"word":"quick","count":1},{"word":"sell","count":1},{"word":"remind","count":1},{"word":"focus","count":1},{"word":"paintings","count":1},{"word":"rebellious","count":1},{"word":"bit","count":1},{"word":"smart","count":1},{"word":"good","count":1},{"word":"lately","count":1},{"word":"wanted","count":1},{"word":"head","count":1},{"word":"work","count":1},{"word":"knew","count":1},{"word":"crack","count":1},{"word":"cause","count":1},{"word":"mess","count":1},{"word":"cut","count":1},{"word":"costs","count":1},{"word":"cooperation","count":1},{"word":"painters","count":1},{"word":"going","count":1},{"word":"shanyun","count":1},{"word":"art","count":1},{"word":"exchange","count":1},{"word":"pretending","count":1},{"word":"boss","count":1},{"word":"mr","count":1},{"word":"baici","count":1},{"word":"wants","count":1},{"word":"business","count":1},{"word":"kept","count":1},{"word":"quiet","count":1},{"word":"stop","count":1},{"word":"talking","count":1},{"word":"staring","count":1},{"word":"wait","count":1},{"word":"i've","count":1},{"word":"told","count":1},{"word":"aaargh","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Who the hell are you?! Coming at us like this... Think you can just push around Exiles, huh?!","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"W-wait a second! Things don't need to get violent! We'll talk, okay?","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"About Mingyan... Didn't my men answer your questions already? That's everything we've got on her, I swear. What more do you want?","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"Alright, alright! I'll tell you everything!","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"What? Can't you see that we're no match for {Male=him;Female=her}? Go ahead and pick a fight if you want, but I'm not risking my life for this.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"Now what else do you want to know? Just ask!","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"Oh, quick to sell me out, huh? All I did was remind her to focus on her paintings.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"She's been rebellious and a bit too smart for her own good lately. I just wanted her to keep her head down and work. Who knew she'd crack and cause that mess.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"To cut our costs and keep our cooperation with the painters going. What else could it be?","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"We... we're with the Shanyun Art Exchange. We're only pretending to be Exiles because our boss, Mr. Baici, wants this business kept quiet.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"You just can't stop talking back, can you?","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"Huh? Why are you staring at me? Wait, I've told you everything I know! Aaargh—","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000}]}